Teyie is Towelead's little sister, just younger by a few months.
Ann was Towelead's annoying classmate from college, they both met for the first time in 6th grade.
Vera supported Towelead when Aloe broke up with him.
Aloe is Vera's best friend. Aloe also left Towelead due to his lack of money, even though Towelead tried his best. He since moved on.
Towelead and Dylan are best friends.
Rine and Eggy are best friends.
Maddison is Rine's older sister.
Ruthabel is the single mother of Maddison and Rine
